  <!--============================ Sephim ===============================-->

  <ThingDef ParentName="RockBase">
    <defName>MineableSephim</defName>
    <label>sephim ore</label>
    <description>Rock containing bits of sephim.

A very sought after material amongs warmongers, Sephim it excellent for use in sharp melee weapons, as its ability to retain a sharp edge, and light weight makes it deadly indeed. It can also be used to good effect in armor, providing excellent protection against piercing attacks. When unprocessed, Sephim can be used tactically to produce a smokescreen when damaged sufficiently.

Dedicated to: SilverSephiroth</description>
